metadata.name: DC Franchise Rankings Database
metadata.source: Percentile-based relative scoring + AI narratives (full 6-season cast)

scoringSystem.overview: Align√© sur la grille DC (S5) + ajustement S6 quand applicable.
notes: Percentiles calculated across the entire database (all 68 players).
Social = combo of low votes against + high jury votes (implemented as juryRate - votesRate).
Strategic = proxy via idols/advantages and any available strategic ranks (when a complete strategic ranking isn't available).
If a DC score exists in PDFs for a player, it can be stored as a reference field (dcScoreS5) but the final ordering here is driven by the weighted percentiles.
